node.text:
You're invited to an exclusive FACEBOOK LIVE AUDIO ROOM event with me MIKE EPPS @realmikeepps, NIA LONG @nialong, NICOLE ARI PARKER @nicoleariparker and SKYLAR DIGGINS-SMITH @skylardiggins. We’re talking about our favorite 90’s movies, music, style and sharing why the era was so iconic. It's all happening TODAY, Wednesday, August 18th at 6pm PT on Facebook.
 
https://facebook.com/events/s/skylars-a-90s-baby/393768912099201/
 
Just click the event link and RSVP to get notified so you can listen to the conversation. Be sure to share the link on your own facebook wall to invite your friends to the room.  See you there.
